23. Quick Difference Between Commands
Command	Purpose
git fetch	Download changes
git pull	Download + merge
git merge	Combine branches
git rebase	Move commits
git reset	Undo commits
git revert	Reverse commit safely
git stash	Temporary save
git checkout	Switch branch/file
git switch	Modern branch switch
24. Emergency Fix Commands
Undo last commit safely
git revert HEAD
Recover deleted branch
git reflog
See all actions history
git reflog
25. Helpful Aliases
Create shortcut aliases
git config --global alias.s status
git config --global alias.c commit
git config --global alias.l "log --oneline --graph"
Usage:

git s
git l

